text: George William Warwick (May 1, 1890 – September 28, 1964Hockey deaths - September 1964) was a Canadian professional ice hockey player. He played with the Montreal Wanderers of the National Hockey Association during the 1913–14 NHA season. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1964 deaths Category:Canadian ice hockey goaltenders Category:Montreal Wanderers (NHA) players Category:Ice hockey people from Ontario
